{#-
  Accordion — orchestrates N Collapsible items with optional single-mode
  mutex + roving tabindex + Arrow / Home / End keyboard navigation between
  triggers.

  Composes N Collapsible children (consumer-provided via the `items` block).
  Each item is a full Collapsible — Accordion does NOT render the triggers
  itself, it just listens to bubbled `collapsible:toggle` events.

  Modes:
    - single  (default) — only ONE Collapsible may be open at a time.
                          Opening one closes the others (mutex).
    - multi             — each Collapsible toggles independently.
                          (Functionally equivalent to N standalone Collapsibles;
                          Accordion still provides the keyboard nav.)

  Keyboard pattern (WAI-ARIA APG "Accordion" pattern, except we omit
  Ctrl+PgUp/Down which is rarely needed for the kit's use cases):
    Tab / Shift+Tab → enter/leave the group on the active trigger.
    Arrow Down       → next trigger (cyclic).
    Arrow Up         → previous trigger (cyclic).
    Home             → first trigger.
    End              → last trigger.
    Enter / Space    → toggle the focused Collapsible (native button activation).

  Parameters:
    htmlId       (string, optional)  — auto-generated.
    mode         (string, optional)  — single (default) | multi.
    className    (string, optional)  — extra utility classes on the wrapper.

  Blocks (one required):
    items — N Collapsible includes. Each Collapsible carries its own controller
            + its own aria-* contract. The Accordion does NOT touch the inner
            ARIA attributes (single source of truth — the inner Collapsible).
-#}

{%- set htmlId    = htmlId    | default('theme-accordion-' ~ random()) -%}
{%- set mode      = mode      | default('single') -%}
{%- set className = className | default('') -%}

{%- set _classes = ['theme-accordion'] -%}
{%- if className -%}{%- set _classes = _classes | merge([className]) -%}{%- endif -%}

<div
  class="{{ _classes | join(' ') }}"
  id="{{ htmlId }}"
  data-controller="accordion"
  data-action="collapsible:toggle->accordion#onChildToggle keydown->accordion#keydown"
  data-accordion-mode-value="{{ mode }}"
  data-mode="{{ mode }}"
>
  {%- block items -%}{%- endblock -%}
</div>
